Class NiftiSFormCoordinateMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • iiv.data.AffineCoordinateMap
      • iiv.data.NiftiSFormCoordinateMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CoordinateMap, iiVScriptable

    public class NiftiSFormCoordinateMap
extends AffineCoordinateMap
    Class that converts coordinates into another space usually scanner-anatomical coordinates based on a scale, translation and a rotation matrix.
    Since:
    iiV1.17a
    See Also:
